rian team had not packed any track bikes.\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1887, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1756, \"end\": 1763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9164412221062399, \"rank\": 0.09117717777685241, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}, {\"begin\": 1842, \"end\": 1850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"score\": 0.995494241606683, \"rank\": 0.004090171348831769, \"text\": \"Nigerian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigerians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The notice\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1752}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 1801, \"to\": 1810}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1814, \"to\": 1832}, {\"ngram\": \"any track bikes\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1886}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In steppedthe German team, who had previously helped out Ukpeseraye's team in the 2022 UCI Track World Championshipswhen they did not have aero bars for the Team Pursuit.\", \"from\": 1888, \"to\": 2058, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1902, \"end\": 1908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"score\": 0.8051584429435249, \"rank\": 0.24182723229915076, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2045, \"end\": 2057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.652788166887175e-27, \"text\": \"Team Pursuit\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ukpeseraye's team\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1962}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2022 UCI Track World\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 1990}, {\"ngram\": \"aero bars\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2036}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time, Ukpeseraye got to ride on a specially-engineered bike designed by the Institut f\\u00fcr Forschung und Entwicklung von Sportger\\u00e4ten (FES), leant to her for the Keirin earlier this week and for Friday's Sprint heat.\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2279, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2198, \"end\": 2201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Functional_electrical_stimulation\", \"score\": 0.8961743411336256, \"rank\": 0.11585430881103391, \"text\": \"FES\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Functional_electrical_stimulation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Functional_electrical_stimulation\"}, {\"begin\": 2225, \"end\": 2231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1247766456415945e-53, \"text\": \"Keirin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ukpeseraye\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2081}, {\"ngram\": \"a specially-engineered bike\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2124}, {\"ngram\": \"the Institut f\\u00fcr Forschung und Entwicklung von Sportger\\u00e4ten\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2196}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday's Sprint heat\", \"from\": 2258, \"to\": 2278}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The latest race content, interviews, features, reviews and expert buying guides, direct to your inbox!\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2383, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The latest race content\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2304}, {\"ngram\": \"interviews\", \"from\": 2306, \"to\": 2316}, {\"ngram\": \"features\", \"from\": 2318, \"to\": 2326}, {\"ngram\": \"reviews\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2335}, {\"ngram\": \"expert buying guides\", \"from\": 2340, \"to\": 2360}, {\"ngram\": \"your inbox\", \"from\": 2372, \"to\": 2382}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The bike was fantastic,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2385, \"to\": 2420, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The bike\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2394}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There are times when they give you a new bike to race, and you will find it difficult because you have not been training with it and are not used to it.\", \"from\": 2421, \"to\": 2574, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2437}, {\"ngram\": \"a new bike\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2467}, {\"ngram\": \"race\", \"from\": 2471, \"to\": 2475}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But for me, when they gave me the bike, the first day I used the bike, it was like I had been using it.\", \"from\": 2575, \"to\": 2678, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bike\", \"from\": 2605, \"to\": 2613}, {\"ngram\": \"the bike\", \"from\": 2636, \"to\": 2644}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was very comfortable on it.\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2708, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I really appreciate them a lot, because they noticed that I am in need and they were able to assist me.\\\"\", \"from\": 2710, \"to\": 2815, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"need\", \"from\": 2777, \"to\": 2781}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ukpeseraye is not new to track cycling, having raced an unusual variety of events including the Team Pursuit, Team Sprint, 500-metre time trial, Keirin and Omnium in international competition, but has only raced Individual Sprint at the Continental Championships, and not regularly.\", \"from\": 2819, \"to\": 3101, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2920, \"end\": 2933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pursuit, Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\"}, {\"begin\": 2920, \"end\": 2933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pursuit, Team\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_pursuit\"}, {\"begin\": 2934, \"end\": 2940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sprint_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.9999991765793064, \"rank\": 7.766770621925015e-07, \"text\": \"Sprint\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sprint_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sprint_Corporation\"}, {\"begin\": 2964, \"end\": 2970, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1247766456415945e-53, \"text\": \"Keirin\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keirin\"}, {\"begin\": 2975, \"end\": 2981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omnium\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9632930524266397e-34, \"text\": \"Omnium\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omnium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Omnium\"}, {\"begin\": 3042, \"end\": 3048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sprint_Corporation\", \"score\": 0.9999991765793064, \"rank\": 7.766770621925015e-07, \"text\": \"Sprint\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sprint_Corporation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sprint_Corporation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ukpeseraye\", \"from\": 2819, \"to\": 2829}, {\"ngram\": \"cycling\", \"from\": 2850, \"to\": 2857}, {\"ngram\": \"an unusual variety\", \"from\": 2872, \"to\": 2890}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 2894, \"to\": 2900}, {\"ngram\": \"500-metre time trial\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 2962}, {\"ngram\": \"international competition\", \"from\": 2985, \"to\": 3010}, {\"ngram\": \"the Continental Championships\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3081}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her results do not reflect her obvious talent, however, because while Nigeria has a wooden velodrome in one of the most expensive sports stadiums in the world, the facility has a history of neglect.\", \"from\": 3103, \"to\": 3301, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3173, \"end\": 3180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9164412221062399, \"rank\": 0.09117717777685241, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her results\", \"from\": 3103, \"to\": 3114}, {\"ngram\": \"her obvious talent\", \"from\": 3130, \"to\": 3148}, {\"ngram\": \"a wooden velodrome\", \"from\": 3185, \"to\": 3203}, {\"ngram\": \"the most expensive sports stadiums\", \"from\": 3214, \"to\": 3248}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3252, \"to\": 3261}, {\"ngram\": \"the facility\", \"from\": 3263, \"to\": 3275}, {\"ngram\": \"a history\", \"from\": 3280, \"to\": 3289}, {\"ngram\": \"neglect\", \"from\": 3293, \"to\": 3300}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although it was refurbished in recent years, the velodrome has been designated as a multi-purpose facility and isrented out for religious services and other events for the equivalent of \\u20ac375 a day.\", \"from\": 3302, \"to\": 3499, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"recent years\", \"from\": 3333, \"to\": 3345}, {\"ngram\": \"the velodrome\", \"from\": 3347, \"to\": 3360}, {\"ngram\": \"a multi-purpose facility\", \"from\": 3384, \"to\": 3408}, {\"ngram\": \"religious services\", \"from\": 3430, \"to\": 3448}, {\"ngram\": \"other events\", \"from\": 3453, \"to\": 3465}, {\"ngram\": \"the equivalent\", \"from\": 3470, \"to\": 3484}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ukpeseraye hoped that her appearance and promising performance at the Olympics would lead to the velodrome being set aside for its intended purpose.\", \"from\": 3501, \"to\": 3649, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ukpeseraye\", \"from\": 3501, \"to\": 3511}, {\"ngram\": \"her appearance\", \"from\": 3523, \"to\": 3537}, {\"ngram\": \"promising performance\", \"from\": 3542, \"to\": 3563}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3567, \"to\": 3579}, {\"ngram\": \"the velodrome\", \"from\": 3594, \"to\": 3607}, {\"ngram\": \"its intended purpose\", \"from\": 3628, \"to\": 3648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have a very beautiful track.\", \"from\": 3651, \"to\": 3683, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very beautiful track\", \"from\": 3660, \"to\": 3682}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our track is the best in Africa, but we do not use it.\", \"from\": 3684, \"to\": 3738, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our track\", \"from\": 3684, \"to\": 3693}, {\"ngram\": \"Africa\", \"from\": 3709, \"to\": 3715}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They do not give us the permission,\\\" Ukpeseraye said.\", \"from\": 3739, \"to\": 3792, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3756, \"to\": 3758}, {\"ngram\": \"the permission\", \"from\": 3759, \"to\": 3773}, {\"ngram\": \"Ukpeseraye\", \"from\": 3776, \"to\": 3786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sometimes we have competition and we want to train in the velodrome but there is a party there and they say we cannot use it, so we take our bikes and we go home.\", \"from\": 3794, \"to\": 3957, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 3813, \"to\": 3824}, {\"ngram\": \"the velodrome\", \"from\": 3849, \"to\": 3862}, {\"ngram\": \"a party\", \"from\": 3876, \"to\": 3883}, {\"ngram\": \"our bikes\", \"from\": 3932, \"to\": 3941}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When we wanted to go to Glasgow for the World Championship, we have to be training on the track.\", \"from\": 3958, \"to\": 4054, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3982, \"end\": 3989, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"score\": 0.9999998777784714, \"rank\": 9.824332614268572e-08, \"text\": \"Glasgow\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow\"}], \"noun_phrases\